text: ao krom robsakhnhom. chaur puok anak anouvotd tamophlauv robsa puok anak choh chamnek khnhom ka anouvotd tamophlauv robsakhnhom der . puok anak kngte nung doeng pi chn del tearounakamm nung thleak towleu ke del thveu aoy ke ameasa ning chn del phout kohk . haey chaur puok anak rngcham meulchoh pitabrakd nasa khnhom ka chea anak rngcham meul cheamuoy puok anak der
